{
    "publish_date": "2012-12-04T08:39:21.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT2M40S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "I guess one of the things you guys are the most curious about is color.", 
            "dur": "2.9", 
            "start": "0"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How does it work for me? What is it?", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I don&#39;t know. ", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, being blind since birth, I&#39;ve never seen color.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I don&#39;t have any concept of what it is.", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "13.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I mean, I&#39;ve never seen anything.", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "15.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But there&#39;s this whole part of vocabulary, of language -", 
            "dur": "2.75", 
            "start": "17.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that doesn&#39;t mean anything to me.", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "20.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Over the years,  people have tried and tried to explain color to me,", 
            "dur": "2.25", 
            "start": "23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I just don&#39;t understand it.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "25.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I think the best way to show you, is to try and explain to someone who&#39;s never heard before,", 
            "dur": "3.5", 
            "start": "28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what the ocean sounds like.", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "32.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Or what the birds sound like.", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "34.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that&#39;s where color is for me.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "36"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&#39;Cause somebody who&#39;s never heard, doesn&#39;t know what those thing are -", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "38"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "has no concept. None.", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "41.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And people will try and explain a sense, with another sense.", 
            "dur": "2.9", 
            "start": "43.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s like the way this smells, maybe, that&#39;s what a particular color...", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "47"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What?", 
            "dur": "1.5", 
            "start": "49.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you&#39;re going to tell me you&#39;re going to explain what color looks like, by my nose?", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That doesn&#39;t make any bloody sense at all.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So when somebody says something&#39;s red to me, ", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "59"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I don&#39;t quite get it.", 
            "dur": "1", 
            "start": "61"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I know that red is fire, or a stoplight is red.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "62"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Or when someone says you&#39;re in the red.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "66"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You know, that means you&#39;re in some trouble, like financial trouble.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Again, just stuff that I picked up from hearing about it.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "72"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I don&#39;t know what it looks like.", 
            "dur": "1", 
            "start": "75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Blue. ", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "77"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Blue as the water is blue. ", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Cold, or ice is blue.", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "81.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The sky is blue.", 
            "dur": "1.5", 
            "start": "83.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now how can the sky and ice be the same thing, that&#39;s weird to me.", 
            "dur": "2.9", 
            "start": "85.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But it&#39;s v...what&#39;s that?", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Same color! Same color, means two completely different things.", 
            "dur": "3.9", 
            "start": "90.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I don&#39;t get it.", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "94.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I hear a lot about orange. ", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "97"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is an orange actually orange? The fruit?", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "99"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I know nothing rhymes with it.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "102"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There&#39;s nothing that rhymes with orange, is there?", 
            "dur": "2.15", 
            "start": "104.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Way to go, orange.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "106.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Way to be involved in poetry and song.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "109"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Black. What&#39;s black? Black is supposed to be all the colors, all smushed together.", 
            "dur": "4", 
            "start": "113"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then white is the absence of color? ", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "118"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So when I hear black and white ...", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "120.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To me they&#39;re just opposites, right? ", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "122.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&#39;Cause one has everything and the other has none. ", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "124.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then there are things that don&#39;t have color.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "127"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Like water. But -", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "130"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It doesn&#39;t have color, but the ocean does? I don&#39;t get that.", 
            "dur": "2.75", 
            "start": "132.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Color is hard. How do sighted people keep &#39;em all straight?", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "\u266a [TXP bumper music]", 
            "dur": "2.9", 
            "start": "139.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I can&#39;t even think of anything that&#39;s indigo. A car. ", 
            "dur": "2.75", 
            "start": "142"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They always have weird colors for cars.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I remember one time a long time ago, I was buying a car with somebody,", 
            "dur": "2.9", 
            "start": "148.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and they said &quot;How about heather mist&quot;. ", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "151"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was like, &quot;What?&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "153.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve never even heard of that. Nothing else in the world is heather mist.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "155"
        }
    ], 
